Automata
public class Automata extends Object

    • addFromFile

      public void addFromFile​(File toRead) throws FileNotFoundException
      This method adds transition, initial state AND final state from a file it calls addFromString for each line of the file
      Parameters:
      toRead - the file to read, the file must contain one line with an init and one line with a final see the readme for more explanation on file creation
      Throws:
      FileNotFoundException - whenever file is not found
